{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775854344556,"sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","part":{"id":"prt_d792ad50d001KMcsIeUS1iEOco","messageID":"msg_d792ac924001kQ9gkRDgkx03Ax","sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_5f991f14003f4b9b81ed0179","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Tasks\n2: \n3: ## Implementation Tasks\n4: \n5: <!-- TODO: 拆分为可执行的实施步骤 -->\n6: \n7: - [ ] Task 1\n8: - [ ] Task 2\n9: - [ ] Task 3\n10: \n11: ## Verification Tasks\n12: \n13: <!-- TODO: 验证步骤 -->\n14: \n15: - [ ] 单元测试\n16: - [ ] 集成测试\n17: - [ ] 手动验证\n\n(End of file - total 17 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Tasks\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n<!-- TODO: 拆分为可执行的实施步骤 -->\n\n- [ ] Task 1\n- [ ] Task 2\n- [ ] Task 3\n\n## Verification Tasks\n\n<!-- TODO: 验证步骤 -->\n\n- [ ] 单元测试\n- [ ] 集成测试\n- [ ] 手动验证","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775854344545,"end":1775854344555}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775854345804,"sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","part":{"id":"prt_d792ad9e6001BuefniI5IiHdeW","messageID":"msg_d792ac924001kQ9gkRDgkx03Ax","sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_ec44e319b2124d68b98edc15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-022: CLI publish 命令 — Delta Spec\n2: \n3: ## Context\n4: \n5: - **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n6: - **Language:** Python\n7: - **Size:** L\n8: - **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n9: \n10: ## Delta Requirements\n11: \n12: ### Requirement: `publish` command entry point\n13: \n14: The system SHALL provide a `publish` subcommand on the Typer application that orchestrates agent deployment to either AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or standard Kubernetes.\n15: \n16: #### Scenario: Command signature and options\n17: - **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and the user runs `agentcube publish --help`\n18: - **WHEN** the help text is displayed\n19: - **THEN** it SHALL show the following options:\n20:   - `-f, --workspace TEXT` — Path to the agent workspace directory (default: `.`)\n21:   - `--version TEXT` — Semantic version string (e.g., v1.0.0)\n22:   - `--image-url TEXT` — Image repository URL (required in local build mode)\n23:   - `--image-username TEXT` — Username for image repository\n24:   - `--image-password TEXT` — Password for image repository\n25:   - `--description TEXT` — Agent description\n26:   - `--region TEXT` — Deployment region\n27:   - `--cloud-provider TEXT` — Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei)\n28:   - `--provider TEXT` — Target provider: `agentcube` (AgentRuntime CR) or `k8s` (Deployment/Service) (default: `agentcube`)\n29:   - `--node-port INTEGER` — Specific NodePort to use (30000-32767) for K8s deployment\n30:   - `--replicas INTEGER` — Number of replicas for K8s deployment (default: 1)\n31:   - `--namespace TEXT` — The namespace for the deployment\n32:   - `--verbose` — Enable detailed logging\n33: \n34: #### Scenario: Default option values\n35: - **GIVEN** the user runs `agentcube publish` with no options\n36: - **WHEN** the command resolves its arguments\n37: - **THEN** the values SHALL be:\n38:   - `workspace` = `\".\"`\n39:   - `version` = `None`\n40:   - `image_url` = `None`\n41:   - `image_username` = `None`\n42:   - `image_password` = `None`\n43:   - `description` = `None`\n44:   - `region` = `None`\n45:   - `cloud_provider` = `None`\n46:   - `provider` = `\"agentcube\"`\n47:   - `node_port` = `None`\n48:   - `replicas` = `None`\n49:   - `namespace` = `None`\n50:   - `verbose` = `False`\n51: \n52: #### Scenario: Workspace path resolution\n53: - **GIVEN** the user provides a workspace path via `-f` or `--workspace`\n54: - **WHEN** the command starts execution\n55: - **THEN** the path SHALL be resolved to an absolute `Path` object before being passed to `PublishRuntime`\n56: \n57: ### Requirement: Provider validation\n58: \n59: The system SHALL validate the `--provider` option and route to the correct publish flow.\n60: \n61: #### Scenario: Valid provider values\n62: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--provider agentcube` or `--provider k8s`\n63: - **WHEN** the command validates the provider\n64: - **THEN** the system SHALL accept the value and instantiate `PublishRuntime` with the corresponding `provider` argument\n65: \n66: #### Scenario: Invalid provider value\n67: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--provider invalid-provider`\n68: - **WHEN** the command validates the provider\n69: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the provider must be `agentcube` or `k8s`\n70: \n71: ### Requirement: Image preparation for publishing\n72: \n73: The system SHALL prepare the container image for deployment by either pushing a local image to a registry or using an explicit image URL from metadata.\n74: \n75: #### Scenario: Image preparation dispatch by build mode\n76: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_image_for_publishing` is called\n77: - **WHEN** `metadata.build_mode` is `local`\n78: - **THEN** it SHALL call `_prepare_local_image` and return the resulting image reference\n79: - **WHEN** `metadata.build_mode` is `cloud`\n80: - **THEN** it SHALL call `_prepare_cloud_image` and return the resulting image reference\n81: \n82: #### Scenario: Local image preparation with CLI credentials\n83: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local` and the user passes `--image-url`, `--image-username`, and `--image-password`\n84: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image` runs\n85: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n86:   1. Call `DockerService._docker_login_sdk` with the provided credentials\n87:   2. Call `DockerService._tag_image_sdk` to tag the local image for the target registry\n88:   3. Call `DockerService.push_image` to push the image to the registry\n89:   4. Return the full image reference (registry URL + image name + tag)\n90: \n91: #### Scenario: Local image preparation without credentials\n92: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local` and no `--image-username`/`--image-password` is provided\n93: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image` runs\n94: - **THEN** it SHALL attempt to push using credentials from metadata (`registry_username`, `registry_password`) if present, or skip login if the registry allows anonymous push\n95: \n96: #### Scenario: Local image preparation requires image URL\n97: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `local` and no `--image-url` is provided\n98: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_local_image` runs\n99: - **THEN** it SHALL check metadata for `image` field; if absent, raise `ValueError` indicating image URL is required for local build mode\n100: \n101: #### Scenario: Cloud image preparation\n102: - **GIVEN** `build_mode` is `cloud`\n103: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._prepare_cloud_image` runs\n104: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n105:   1. Resolve the image reference from metadata `image` field or `--image-url`\n106:   2. Return the image reference without performing Docker operations\n107: \n108: ### Requirement: AgentCube provider (AgentRuntime CR) publish flow\n109: \n110: The system SHALL deploy an AgentRuntime custom resource to Kubernetes when `provider` is `agentcube`.\n111: \n112: #### Scenario: AgentCube prerequisites — required URLs\n113: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube`\n114: - **WHEN** metadata lacks `router_url` or `workload_manager_url`\n115: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` with a message requiring both fields in `agent_metadata.yaml`\n116: \n117: #### Scenario: AgentCube prerequisites — readiness probe fields\n118: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube`\n119: - **WHEN** metadata lacks `readiness_probe_path` or `readiness_probe_port`\n120: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise `ValueError` indicating readiness probe configuration is required\n121: \n122: #### Scenario: Successful AgentRuntime CR deployment\n123: - **GIVEN** all prerequisites are met and `provider` is `agentcube`\n124: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n125: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n126:   1. Prepare the image reference via `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n127:   2. Call `AgentCubeProvider.deploy_agent_runtime` with `agent_name`, `image_url`, `port`, `entrypoint`, `env_vars`, `workload_manager_url`, `router_url`, `readiness_probe_path`, `readiness_probe_port`\n128:   3. Update metadata with deployment info via `_update_publish_metadata`\n129:   4. Return a dict with `status`, `agent_name`, `namespace`, `agent_id`\n130: \n131: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with namespace override\n132: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--namespace production`\n133: - **WHEN** `AgentCubeProvider` is instantiated\n134: - **THEN** it SHALL use `production` as the namespace instead of the default `default`\n135: \n136: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with version override\n137: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--version v2.0.0`\n138: - **WHEN** `_publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n139: - **THEN** it SHALL update `metadata.version` to `v2.0.0` before deployment\n140: \n141: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with description override\n142: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--description \"My updated agent\"`\n143: - **WHEN** `_publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n144: - **THEN** it SHALL update `metadata.description` before deployment\n145: \n146: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR deployment with region\n147: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--region cn-north-4`\n148: - **WHEN** `_publish_cr_to_k8s` runs\n149: - **THEN** it SHALL update `metadata.region` before deployment\n150: \n151: ### Requirement: Standard Kubernetes provider publish flow\n152: \n153: The system SHALL deploy a standard Kubernetes Deployment and NodePort Service when `provider` is `k8s`.\n154: \n155: #### Scenario: Successful K8s deployment\n156: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `k8s` and Kubernetes client initializes\n157: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._publish_k8s` runs\n158: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n159:   1. Prepare the image reference via `_prepare_image_for_publishing`\n160:   2. Call `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent` with `agent_name`, `image_url`, `port`, `entrypoint`, `replicas`, `node_port`, `env_vars`\n161:   3. Call `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready` with `timeout=120`\n162:   4. Update metadata with deployment info via `_update_publish_metadata`\n163:   5. Return a dict with `status`, `deployment_name`, `service_name`, `namespace`, `node_port`, `service_url`\n164: \n165: #### Scenario: K8s deployment with replicas override\n166: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--replicas 3`\n167: - **WHEN** `_publish_k8s` calls `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent`\n168: - **THEN** it SHALL pass `replicas=3` instead of the default `1`\n169: \n170: #### Scenario: K8s deployment with NodePort override\n171: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 30080`\n172: - **WHEN** `_publish_k8s` calls `KubernetesProvider.deploy_agent`\n173: - **THEN** it SHALL pass `node_port=30080` and the resulting `service_url` SHALL be `http://localhost:30080`\n174: \n175: #### Scenario: K8s deployment readiness timeout\n176: - **GIVEN** the deployment does not become ready within 120 seconds\n177: - **WHEN** `KubernetesProvider.wait_for_deployment_ready` exceeds the timeout\n178: - **THEN** it SHALL raise `TimeoutError` and the system SHALL record the error in metadata before raising `RuntimeError`\n179: \n180: #### Scenario: K8s deployment with namespace override\n181: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--namespace staging`\n182: - **WHEN** `KubernetesProvider` is instantiated\n183: - **THEN** it SHALL use `staging` as the namespace for all resource creation\n184: \n185: ### Requirement: Publish metadata update\n186: \n187: The system SHALL update workspace metadata with publish results upon successful deployment.\n188: \n189: #### Scenario: Update publish metadata on success\n190: - **GIVEN** a successful publish (either provider)\n191: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime._update_publish_metadata` runs\n192: - **THEN** it SHALL:\n193:   1. Update `metadata.agent_id` with the assigned agent ID\n194:   2. Update `metadata.agent_endpoint` with the service URL\n195:   3. Update `metadata.k8s_deployment` with provider-specific deployment info\n196:   4. Persist the updated metadata to `agent_metadata.yaml` via `MetadataService.save_metadata`\n197: \n198: #### Scenario: K8s deployment metadata structure\n199: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `k8s` and publish succeeds\n200: - **WHEN** `_update_publish_metadata` runs\n201: - **THEN** `metadata.k8s_deployment` SHALL include:\n202:   - `type`: `\"Deployment\"`\n203:   - `deployment_name`: the deployment name\n204:   - `service_name`: the service name\n205:   - `namespace`: the namespace\n206:   - `node_port`: the assigned NodePort\n207:   - `service_url`: the service URL\n208: \n209: #### Scenario: AgentRuntime CR metadata structure\n210: - **GIVEN** `provider` is `agentcube` and publish succeeds\n211: - **WHEN** `_update_publish_metadata` runs\n212: - **THEN** `metadata.k8s_deployment` SHALL include:\n213:   - `type`: `\"AgentRuntime\"`\n214:   - `agent_name`: the agent name\n215:   - `namespace`: the namespace\n216:   - `agent_id`: the assigned agent ID\n217: \n218: ### Requirement: CLI success output\n219: \n220: The system SHALL display a Rich-formatted success message after a successful publish.\n221: \n222: #### Scenario: Successful publish output — AgentCube provider\n223: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` completes without exception with `provider=agentcube`\n224: - **WHEN** the `publish` command finishes\n225: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print:\n226:   - A success message with the agent name\n227:   - The resolved workspace path\n228:   - The agent ID\n229:   - The agent endpoint URL\n230:   - Using Rich markup for formatting\n231: \n232: #### Scenario: Successful publish output — K8s provider\n233: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` completes without exception with `provider=k8s`\n234: - **WHEN** the `publish` command finishes\n235: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL print:\n236:   - A success message with the agent name\n237:   - The resolved workspace path\n238:   - The deployment name and service name\n239:   - The service URL (e.g., `http://localhost:{node_port}`)\n240:   - Using Rich markup for formatting\n241: \n242: #### Scenario: Verbose publish output\n243: - **GIVEN** `--verbose` is passed\n244: - **WHEN** the publish runs\n245: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL display detailed logging including:\n246:   - Provider selection\n247:   - Image preparation steps\n248:   - Deployment progress\n249:   - Metadata update confirmation\n250: \n251: ### Requirement: Error handling\n252: \n253: The system SHALL handle publish failures gracefully with appropriate error messages.\n254: \n255: #### Scenario: Publish error with verbose flag\n256: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` raises an exception\n257: - **WHEN** `--verbose` is `True`\n258: - **THEN** `_handle_error` SHALL:\n259:   1. Print `Error publishing agent: {e}` in red\n260:   2. Print a full traceback\n261:   3. Exit with code `1`\n262: \n263: #### Scenario: Publish error without verbose flag\n264: - **GIVEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` raises an exception\n265: - **WHEN** `--verbose` is `False`\n266: - **THEN** `_handle_error` SHALL:\n267:   1. Print `Error publishing agent: {e}` in red\n268:   2. Exit with code `1` (no traceback)\n269: \n270: #### Scenario: Missing workspace\n271: - **GIVEN** the workspace path does not exist\n272: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` is called\n273: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` with a message indicating the workspace directory does not exist\n274: \n275: #### Scenario: Missing metadata file\n276: - **GIVEN** `agent_metadata.yaml` does not exist in the workspace\n277: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` attempts to load metadata\n278: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating the workspace must be packaged first\n279: \n280: ### Requirement: Progress indication\n281: \n282: The system SHALL display a Rich `Progress` spinner during the publish operation.\n283: \n284: #### Scenario: Progress spinner during publish\n285: - **GIVEN** the publish command is running\n286: - **WHEN** `PublishRuntime.publish` is executing\n287: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL show a Rich `Progress` spinner with the text `\"Publishing agent...\"`\n288: \n289: #### Scenario: Progress completion\n290: - **GIVEN** the publish completes successfully\n291: - **WHEN** the spinner stops\n292: - **THEN** the CLI SHALL replace the spinner with a success checkmark and summary\n293: \n294: ### Requirement: NodePort validation\n295: \n296: The system SHALL validate the `--node-port` value when provided for K8s deployments.\n297: \n298: #### Scenario: Valid NodePort range\n299: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 30080`\n300: - **WHEN** the command validates the node port\n301: - **THEN** the system SHALL accept the value (within 30000-32767 range)\n302: \n303: #### Scenario: Invalid NodePort — below range\n304: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 29999`\n305: - **WHEN** the command validates the node port\n306: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\n307: \n308: #### Scenario: Invalid NodePort — above range\n309: - **GIVEN** the user passes `--node-port 32768`\n310: - **WHEN** the command validates the node port\n311: - **THEN** the system SHALL raise a `ValueError` indicating NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\n312: \n313: ## File changes\n314: \n315: | Action | File | Description |\n316: |--------|------|-------------|\n317: | Modify | `agentcube/cli/main.py` | Add `publish` Typer command with options, provider routing, and error handling |\n318: | Modify | `agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py` | Implement `publish`, `_publish_cr_to_k8s`, `_publish_k8s`, `_prepare_image_for_publishing`, `_prepare_local_image`, `_prepare_cloud_image`, `_update_publish_metadata` |\n319: | Modify | `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` | Ensure `push_image`, `_docker_login_sdk`, `_tag_image_sdk` support publish workflow |\n320: | Modify | `agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` | Ensure `deploy_agent_runtime` supports all publish parameters |\n321: | Modify | `agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` | Ensure `deploy_agent` and `wait_for_deployment_ready` support publish workflow |\n322: | Modify | `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py` | Ensure metadata save supports publish workflow |\n323: | Add | `tests/cli/test_publish.py` | CLI publish command tests |\n324: | Add | `tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` | PublishRuntime unit tests |\n\n(End of file - total 324 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令 — Delta Spec\n\n## Context\n\n- **Module:** `cmd/cli`\n- **Language:** Python\n- **Size:** L\n- **Base specs:** `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## Delta Requirements\n\n### Requirement: `publish` command entry point\n\nThe system SHALL provide a `publish` subcommand on the Typer application that orchestrates agent deployment to either AgentCube (AgentRuntime CR) or standard Kubernetes.\n\n#### Scenario: Command signature and options\n- **GIVEN** the CLI is installed and the user runs `agentcube publish --help`\n- **WHEN** the help text is displayed\n- **THEN** it SHALL show the following options:\n  - `-f, --workspace TEXT` — Path to the agent workspace directory (default: `.`)","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775854345795,"end":1775854345802}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775854346972,"sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","part":{"id":"prt_d792adec4001zds5H5s9KBXEFy","messageID":"msg_d792ac924001kQ9gkRDgkx03Ax","sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_2c2402f4db3247a581e27178","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-021 — CLI build 命令 — Tasks\n2: \n3: > **Module:** cmd/cli\n4: > **Language:** Python\n5: > **Size:** M\n6: > **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n7: > **Reference:** `changes/AR-021/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-021/design.md`, `changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n8: \n9: ## T1. 实现 DockerService — Docker 守护进程检查与镜像构建\n10: \n11: - [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n12: - [ ] 1.2 定义 `DockerService` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n13: - [ ] 1.3 实现 `check_docker_available(self) -> bool`：\n14:   - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n15:   - 调用 `client.ping()` 检查守护进程\n16:   - 异常时返回 `False`\n17: - [ ] 1.4 实现 `build_image(self, dockerfile_path: Path, context_path: Path, image_name: str, tag: str = \"latest\", build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Dict[str, str]`：\n18:   - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n19:   - 记录 `start_time = time.time()`\n20:   - 调用 `client.images.build(path=str(context_path), dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path), tag=f\"{image_name}:{tag}\", buildargs=build_args)`\n21:   - 计算 `build_time = time.time() - start_time`\n22:   - 获取镜像信息 `client.images.get(image.id)`\n23:   - 返回 dict：`{\"image_name\": image_name, \"image_id\": image.short_id, \"image_size\": self._format_size(...), \"build_time\": f\"{build_time:.2f}s\"}`\n24: - [ ] 1.5 实现 `_format_size(self, size_bytes: int) -> str`：\n25:   - 将字节数格式化为人类可读字符串（如 `\"123.4 MB\"`）\n26:   - 单位：B, KB, MB, GB\n27: - [ ] 1.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py`\n28: - [ ] 1.7 测试 `TestDockerService_CheckDockerAvailable_Running`：Docker 运行中 → 返回 `True`\n29: - [ ] 1.8 测试 `TestDockerService_CheckDockerAvailable_NotRunning`：Docker 未运行 → 返回 `False`\n30: - [ ] 1.9 测试 `TestDockerService_BuildImage_Success`：成功构建 → 返回正确结果 dict\n31: - [ ] 1.10 测试 `TestDockerService_BuildImage_WithProxy`：传入 proxy build_args → `buildargs` 包含 `HTTP_PROXY` 和 `HTTPS_PROXY`\n32: - [ ] 1.11 测试 `TestDockerService_BuildImage_Failure`：Dockerfile 错误 → 抛出 `docker.errors.BuildError`\n33: - [ ] 1.12 测试 `TestDockerService_FormatSize_Bytes`：`0` → `\"0 B\"`\n34: - [ ] 1.13 测试 `TestDockerService_FormatSize_KB`：`1024` → `\"1.0 KB\"`\n35: - [ ] 1.14 测试 `TestDockerService_FormatSize_MB`：`1048576` → `\"1.0 MB\"`\n36: - [ ] 1.15 测试 `TestDockerService_FormatSize_GB`：`1073741824` → `\"1.0 GB\"`\n37: \n38: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py -v` 全部通过\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T2. 实现 BuildRuntime 类骨架与 build() 主编排方法\n43: \n44: - [ ] 2.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py`\n45: - [ ] 2.2 定义 `BuildRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`，存储 `self.verbose` 和 `self.metadata_service = MetadataService(verbose=verbose)`\n46: - [ ] 2.3 实现 `build(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]` 主编排方法：\n47:   - 1. 加载元数据：`metadata = self.metadata_service.load_metadata(workspace_path)`，如为 None 则 `raise ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged. Run 'pack' first.\")`\n48:   - 2. 保存原始版本号：`original_version = metadata.version`\n49:   - 3. 自增版本号：`self._increment_version(workspace_path, metadata)`\n50:   - 4. try 块内：\n51:     - 前置校验：`self._validate_build_prerequisites(workspace_path, metadata)`\n52:     - 根据 build_mode 分发：`local` → `_build_local()`，`cloud` → `_build_cloud()`\n53:     - 更新元数据：`self._update_build_metadata(workspace_path, metadata, build_result, tag)`\n54:     - 返回 build_result\n55:   - 5. except 块内：回滚版本号 `metadata.version = original_version`，`self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)`，重新抛出异常\n56: - [ ] 2.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime.py`\n57: - [ ] 2.5 测试 `TestBuildRuntime_UnpackagedWorkspace`：无 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged...\")`\n58: - [ ] 2.6 测试 `TestBuildRuntime_LocalBuild_Success`：local 模式，所有前置条件满足 → 成功返回结果\n59: - [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestBuildRuntime_CloudBuild_Success`：cloud 模式 → 调用 `_build_cloud`\n60: - [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestBuildRuntime_BuildFailure_VersionRollback`：构建失败 → 版本号回滚到原始值\n61: - [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestBuildRuntime_BuildFailure_MetadataSaved`：构建失败回滚后 → 元数据已保存\n62: \n63: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime.py -v` 全部通过（T3-T6 方法可用 mock 替代）\n64: \n65: ---\n66: \n67: ## T3. 实现版本号自增 — BuildRuntime._increment_version\n68: \n69: - [ ] 3.1 实现 `_increment_version(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n70:   - `current = metadata.version`\n71:   - 如 `current` 为 None 或空字符串 → `metadata.version = \"0.0.1\"`\n72:   - 如匹配 `^\\d+\\.\\d+\\.\\d+$`（标准 semver）→ patch 自增：`X.Y.Z` → `X.Y.(Z+1)`\n73:   - 否则尝试 `semver.Version.parse(current)` → 成功则 `v.bump_patch()`\n74:   - `semver.Version.parse` 失败 → `metadata.version = f\"{current}-1\"`\n75: - [ ] 3.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_version.py`\n76: - [ ] 3.3 测试 `TestIncrementVersion_Semver_Patch`：`\"1.2.3\"` → `\"1.2.4\"`\n77: - [ ] 3.4 测试 `TestIncrementVersion_Semver_ZeroPatch`：`\"1.0.0\"` → `\"1.0.1\"`\n78: - [ ] 3.5 测试 `TestIncrementVersion_None`：`None` → `\"0.0.1\"`\n79: - [ ] 3.6 测试 `TestIncrementVersion_Empty`：`\"\"` → `\"0.0.1\"`\n80: - [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestIncrementVersion_NonSemver`：`\"1.0-beta\"` → `\"1.0-beta-1\"`（semver parse 失败 fallback）\n81: - [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestIncrementVersion_SemverLibrary`：`\"1.0.0\"` 使用 semver 库 → `\"1.0.1\"`\n82: \n83: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_version.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Version increment 全部 3 个场景\n84: \n85: ---\n86: \n87: ## T4. 实现构建前置条件校验 — BuildRuntime._validate_build_prerequisites\n88: \n89: - [ ] 4.1 实现 `_validate_build_prerequisites(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata) -> None`：\n90:   - 检查 `agent_metadata.yaml` 存在 → 无则 `ValueError(f\"Metadata file not found: {workspace_path / 'agent_metadata.yaml'}\")`\n91:   - 检查 `Dockerfile` 存在 → 无则 `ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found. Run 'pack' first.\")`\n92:   - 如 `metadata.build_mode == \"local\"`：\n93:     - 创建 `DockerService` 实例\n94:     - 调用 `check_docker_available()` → 返回 False 则 `raise RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n95: - [ ] 4.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_prerequisites.py`\n96: - [ ] 4.3 测试 `TestValidatePrerequisites_MetadataMissing`：无 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `ValueError`\n97: - [ ] 4.4 测试 `TestValidatePrerequisites_DockerfileMissing`：无 `Dockerfile` → `ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found...\")`\n98: - [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestValidatePrerequisites_DockerNotAvailable`：local 模式，Docker 不可用 → `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available...\")`\n99: - [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestValidatePrerequisites_AllPresent_Local`：所有文件存在，Docker 可用，local 模式 → 无异常\n100: - [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestValidatePrerequisites_CloudMode_SkipDockerCheck`：cloud 模式 → 不检查 Docker 可用性\n101: \n102: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_prerequisites.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Build prerequisites validation 全部 3 个场景\n103: \n104: ---\n105: \n106: ## T5. 实现本地 Docker 构建 — BuildRuntime._build_local\n107: \n108: - [ ] 5.1 实现 `_build_local(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n109:   - 解析 image_name：`metadata.image.get(\"name\", metadata.agent_name)`（如 `metadata.image` 为 None 则用 `metadata.agent_name`）\n110:   - 解析 tag：`metadata.version or \"latest\"`\n111:   - 构建 build_args：如 `options.get(\"proxy\")` 非 None → `{\"HTTP_PROXY\": proxy, \"HTTPS_PROXY\": proxy}`\n112:   - 创建 `DockerService` 实例\n113:   - 调用 `docker_service.build_image(dockerfile_path=workspace_path/\"Dockerfile\", context_path=workspace_path, image_name=image_name, tag=tag, build_args=build_args)`\n114:   - 返回构建结果\n115: - [ ] 5.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_local.py`\n116: - [ ] 5.3 测试 `TestBuildLocal_Success`：成功构建 → 返回 `{\"image_name\", \"image_id\", \"image_size\", \"build_time\"}`\n117: - [ ] 5.4 测试 `TestBuildLocal_WithProxy`：`--proxy http://proxy:8080` → `build_args` 包含 `HTTP_PROXY` 和 `HTTPS_PROXY`\n118: - [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestBuildLocal_WithoutProxy`：无 proxy → `build_args=None`\n119: - [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestBuildLocal_ImageNameFromMetadata`：`metadata.image = {\"name\": \"custom-image\"}` → 使用 `\"custom-image\"`\n120: - [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestBuildLocal_ImageNameFromAgentName`：`metadata.image = None` → 使用 `metadata.agent_name`\n121: - [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestBuildLocal_TagFromVersion`：`metadata.version = \"1.2.4\"` → tag 为 `\"1.2.4\"`\n122: - [ ] 5.9 测试 `TestBuildLocal_TagDefaultLatest`：`metadata.version = None` → tag 为 `\"latest\"`\n123: - [ ] 5.10 测试 `TestBuildLocal_DockerBuildError`：`DockerService.build_image` 抛 `BuildError` → 异常传播\n124: \n125: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_local.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Local Docker build 全部场景\n126: \n127: ---\n128: \n129: ## T6. 实现云端构建 — BuildRuntime._build_cloud\n130: \n131: - [ ] 6.1 实现 `_build_cloud(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n132:   - 解析 `cloud_provider = options.get(\"cloud_provider\")`\n133:   - 如 `cloud_provider` 为 None 且 metadata 中无 provider 配置 → `raise ValueError(\"Cloud provider must be specified. Use --cloud-provider option.\")`\n134:   - 记录 verbose 日志：`\"Starting cloud build with provider: {cloud_provider}\"`\n135:   - 返回占位结果 dict（云端构建为异步，返回 job_id）：\n136:     ```python\n137:     {\n138:         \"image_name\": metadata.agent_name,\n139:         \"image_id\": \"pending\",\n140:         \"image_size\": \"N/A\",\n141:         \"build_time\": \"N/A\",\n142:         \"cloud_provider\": cloud_provider,\n143:         \"job_id\": f\"build-{metadata.agent_name}-{int(time.time())}\",\n144:     }\n145:     ```\n146: - [ ] 6.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_cloud.py`\n147: - [ ] 6.3 测试 `TestBuildCloud_WithProvider`：`--cloud-provider huawei` → 返回包含 `cloud_provider` 和 `job_id` 的结果\n148: - [ ] 6.4 测试 `TestBuildCloud_NoProvider`：无 provider → `ValueError(\"Cloud provider must be specified...\")`\n149: - [ ] 6.5 测试 `TestBuildCloud_MetadataProvider`：metadata 中有 provider 配置 → 使用 metadata 中的 provider\n150: - [ ] 6.6 测试 `TestBuildCloud_VerboseLogging`：verbose=True → 记录 provider 信息\n151: \n152: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_cloud.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Cloud build 全部场景\n153: \n154: ---\n155: \n156: ## T7. 实现构建元数据更新 — BuildRuntime._update_build_metadata\n157: \n158: - [ ] 7.1 实现 `_update_build_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata: AgentMetadata, build_result: Dict[str, Any], tag: str) -> None`：\n159:   - 构建 image dict：\n160:     ```python\n161:     image_info = {\n162:         \"name\": build_result.get(\"image_name\", metadata.agent_name),\n163:         \"id\": build_result.get(\"image_id\"),\n164:         \"tag\": tag,\n165:     }\n166:     ```\n167:   - 如 `build_result` 含 `build_time` → `image_info[\"build_time\"] = build_result[\"build_time\"]`\n168:   - 更新 metadata：`metadata = metadata.model_copy(update={\"image\": image_info})`\n169:   - 保存：`self.metadata_service.save_metadata(workspace_path, metadata)`\n170: - [ ] 7.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_metadata.py`\n171: - [ ] 7.3 测试 `TestUpdateBuildMetadata_LocalBuild`：本地构建结果 → `metadata.image` 包含 name, id, tag\n172: - [ ] 7.4 测试 `TestUpdateBuildMetadata_WithTag`：`tag=\"v1.2.4\"` → `image[\"tag\"] = \"v1.2.4\"`\n173: - [ ] 7.5 测试 `TestUpdateBuildMetadata_WithBuildTime`：结果含 `build_time` → `image[\"build_time\"]` 存在\n174: - [ ] 7.6 测试 `TestUpdateBuildMetadata_Persisted`：保存后重新加载 → image 信息一致\n175: - [ ] 7.7 测试 `TestUpdateBuildMetadata_CloudBuild`：云端构建结果 → 正确保存（image_id 为 \"pending\"）\n176: \n177: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_build_runtime_metadata.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Build metadata update 全部场景\n178: \n179: ---\n180: \n181: ## T8. 实现 CLI build 命令入口 — agentcube/cli/main.py\n182: \n183: - [ ] 8.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加 `build` 命令导入：\n184:   - `from agentcube.runtime.build_runtime import BuildRuntime`\n185: - [ ] 8.2 实现 `@app.command()` build 命令：\n186:   - 选项：\n187:     - `workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", help=\"Path to the agent workspace directory.\", show_default=True)`\n188:     - `proxy: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"-p\", \"--proxy\", help=\"Custom proxy URL for dependency resolution.\")`\n189:     - `cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", help=\"Cloud provider name (e.g., huawei).\")`\n190:     - `output: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--output\", help=\"Output path for build artifacts.\")`\n191:     - `verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", help=\"Enable detailed logging.\")`\n192:   - 使用 Rich `Progress` + `SpinnerColumn` 显示 `\"Building agent...\"`\n193:   - 调用 `BuildRuntime(verbose=verbose).build(workspace_path, proxy=proxy, cloud_provider=cloud_provider, output=output)`\n194:   - 成功时 Rich 输出：\n195:     ```\n196:     ✓ Agent '{agent_name}' built successfully!\n197:       Image:  {image_name}:{tag}\n198:       Size:   {image_size}\n199:       Time:   {build_time}\n200:     ```\n201:   - 异常时调用 `_handle_error(e, \"building agent\", verbose)`\n202: - [ ] 8.3 更新 `agentcube/__init__.py` 导出：添加 `BuildRuntime`\n203: - [ ] 8.4 更新 `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` 重新导出 `BuildRuntime`\n204: - [ ] 8.5 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_build_command.py`\n205: - [ ] 8.6 测试 `TestBuildCommand_DefaultOptions`：无选项 → 使用默认 workspace `.`\n206: - [ ] 8.7 测试 `TestBuildCommand_CustomWorkspace`：`-f /path/to/workspace` → 使用指定路径\n207: - [ ] 8.8 测试 `TestBuildCommand_AllOptions`：传递全部选项 → 正确传递给 BuildRuntime\n208: - [ ] 8.9 测试 `TestBuildCommand_SuccessOutput`：成功时显示 image_name, tag, image_size, build_time\n209: - [ ] 8.10 测试 `TestBuildCommand_ErrorNoVerbose`：失败无 verbose → 显示红色错误，无 traceback\n210: - [ ] 8.11 测试 `TestBuildCommand_ErrorVerbose`：失败有 verbose → 显示红色错误 + traceback\n211: - [ ] 8.12 测试 `TestBuildCommand_ExitCodeOnError`：失败 → exit code 1\n212: - [ ] 8.13 测试 `TestBuildCommand_ProgressSpinner`：执行期间显示 Progress spinner\n213: - [ ] 8.14 测试 `TestBuildCommand_HelpOutput`：`build --help` 显示全部 5 个选项\n214: \n215: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_build_command.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §CLI success output 和 §Error handling 全部场景\n216: \n217: ---\n218: \n219: ## T9. 端到端集成测试\n220: \n221: - [ ] 9.1 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/integration/test_build_e2e.py`\n222: - [ ] 9.2 测试 `TestBuildE2E_LocalBuild_FullFlow`：对已 pack 的 hello-agent 示例运行 build → 成功（需 Docker 可用，可 skip）\n223: - [ ] 9.3 测试 `TestBuildE2E_UnpackagedWorkspace`：对未 pack 的工作区运行 build → 错误退出\n224: - [ ] 9.4 测试 `TestBuildE2E_CliOverrides`：使用 `--proxy`, `--cloud-provider` 覆盖 → 正确传递\n225: - [ ] 9.5 测试 `TestBuildE2E_CloudBuild`：使用 `--cloud-provider huawei` → 返回 job_id\n226: - [ ] 9.6 测试 `TestBuildE2E_InvalidWorkspace`：对非目录路径运行 build → 错误退出\n227: - [ ] 9.7 测试 `TestBuildE2E_VersionIncrement`：连续两次 build → 版本号递增\n228: - [ ] 9.8 测试 `TestBuildE2E_MetadataUpdated`：build 成功后 → `agent_metadata.yaml` 包含 image 信息\n229: \n230: **Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/integration/test_build_e2e.py -v` 全部通过（Docker 依赖的测试可标记 skip）\n231: \n232: ---\n233: \n234: ## T10. 代码质量门禁与最终验证\n235: \n236: - [ ] 10.1 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无 lint 错误\n237: - [ ] 10.2 运行 `ruff format --check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认格式合规\n238: - [ ] 10.3 运行 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无类型错误\n239: - [ ] 10.4 运行 `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` 确认覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n240: - [ ] 10.5 确认 T/C 比率 > 0.4（测试代码行数 / 源代码行数）\n241: - [ ] 10.6 运行 `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` 确认安装成功\n242: - [ ] 10.7 运行 `kubectl-agentcube --help` 确认帮助输出包含 build 命令\n243: - [ ] 10.8 运行 `kubectl-agentcube build --help` 确认 build 选项完整（workspace, proxy, cloud-provider, output, verbose）\n244: - [ ] 10.9 确认 `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 有对应测试文件\n245: - [ ] 10.10 确认 `agentcube/runtime/build_runtime.py` 有对应测试文件\n246: - [ ] 10.11 确认 `agentcube/cli/main.py` 的 build 命令有对应测试文件\n247: - [ ] 10.12 确认无 `print()` 用于业务逻辑输出（仅使用 Rich console）\n248: \n249: **Verification:** 以上 12 项全部通过；exit code 均为 0\n250: \n251: ---\n252: \n253: ## Task Dependencies\n254: \n255: ```\n256: T1 (DockerService) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n257:                                                                     │\n258: T2 (BuildRuntime 骨架 + build 编排) ←───────────────────────────────┘\n259:   │\n260:   ├── T3 (版本号自增) ──────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n261:   │                                                                 │\n262:   ├── T4 (前置条件校验) ←── T1 ─────────────────────────────────────┤\n263:   │                                                                 │\n264:   ├── T5 (本地构建) ←── T1 ─────────────────────────────────────────┤\n265:   │                                                                 │\n266:   ├── T6 (云端构建) ────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n267:   │                                                                 │\n268:   └── T7 (元数据更新) ──────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n269:                                                                     │\n270: T8 (CLI build 命令) ←── T2, T3, T4, T5, T6, T7 ─────────────────────┘\n271:   │\n272: T9 (E2E 集成测试) ←── T8 ───────────────────────────────────────────┘\n273:   │\n274: T10 (质量门禁)\n275: ```\n276: \n277: **Parallel execution:**\n278: - T1（DockerService）可独立开始，不依赖其他任务\n279: - T2（BuildRuntime 骨架）可在 T1 进行中开始（使用 mock DockerService）\n280: - T3（版本号自增）仅依赖 T2 的类骨架，可并行开发\n281: - T4（前置条件校验）需 T1 完成后开始（依赖 DockerService.check_docker_available）\n282: - T5（本地构建）需 T1 完成后开始（依赖 DockerService.build_image）\n283: - T6（云端构建）不依赖 T1，可与 T4、T5 并行开发\n284: - T7（元数据更新）仅依赖 T2 的类骨架和 MetadataService（已有），可并行开发\n285: - T3、T4、T5、T6、T7 可并行开发（在 T2 骨架和 T1 完成后）\n286: - T8（CLI 命令）需 T2-T7 全部完成后开始\n287: - T9（E2E 集成测试）需 T8 完成后开始\n288: - T10（质量门禁）需所有前置任务完成\n289: \n290: ---\n291: \n292: ## Acceptance Criteria\n293: \n294: | # | Criterion | Command |\n295: |---|-----------|---------|\n296: | AC1 | build 命令接受所有指定选项 | `kubectl-agentcube build --help` 显示 workspace, proxy, cloud-provider, output, verbose |\n297: | AC2 | workspace 默认 `.` | `kubectl-agentcube build` 使用当前目录 |\n298: | AC3 | proxy 通过 `-p` / `--proxy` 指定 | `kubectl-agentcube build -p http://proxy:8080` → build_args 包含 proxy |\n299: | AC4 | 未 pack 的工作区报错 | 无 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged...\")` |\n300: | AC5 | Dockerfile 不存在报错 | 无 `Dockerfile` → `ValueError(\"Dockerfile not found. Run 'pack' first.\")` |\n301: | AC6 | local 模式 Docker 不可用报错 | Docker 未运行 → `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")` |\n302: | AC7 | 版本号自增：semver | `\"1.2.3\"` → `\"1.2.4\"` |\n303: | AC8 | 版本号自增：无版本 | `None` → `\"0.0.1\"` |\n304: | AC9 | 版本号自增：非标准格式 | `\"1.0-beta\"` → `\"1.0-beta-1\"` |\n305: | AC10 | 构建失败版本号回滚 | 构建异常 → version 恢复为原始值 |\n306: | AC11 | cloud 模式无 provider 报错 | 无 `--cloud-provider` → `ValueError(\"Cloud provider must be specified...\")` |\n307: | AC12 | 构建成功更新 metadata.image | `agent_metadata.yaml` 包含 image name, id, tag |\n308: | AC13 | 成功消息显示镜像信息 | Rich 格式输出 image_name:tag, size, build_time |\n309: | AC14 | 错误处理打印红色消息 + traceback（verbose），退出码 1 | `_handle_error` 行为正确 |\n310: | AC15 | Rich Progress spinner 在执行期间显示 | 显示 `\"Building agent...\"` |\n311: | AC16 | proxy 作为 Docker build_args 传递 | `HTTP_PROXY` 和 `HTTPS_PROXY` 传入 `client.images.build` |\n312: | AC17 | 覆盖率 ≥ 80% | `pytest --cov=agentcube` |\n313: | AC18 | T/C 比率 > 0.4 | 测试代码行数 / 源代码行数 |\n314: | AC19 | ruff lint 无错误 | `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n315: | AC20 | mypy 类型检查无错误 | `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` |\n316: | AC21 | console script 可用 | `kubectl-agentcube build --help` 正常输出 |\n\n(End of file - total 316 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-021 — CLI build 命令 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** cmd/cli\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** M\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-021/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-021/design.md`, `changes/AR-021/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## T1. 实现 DockerService — Docker 守护进程检查与镜像构建\n\n- [ ] 1.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py`\n- [ ] 1.2 定义 `DockerService` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False)`\n- [ ] 1.3 实现 `check_docker_available(self) -> bool`：\n  - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n  - 调用 `client.ping()` 检查守护进程\n  - 异常时返回 `False`\n- [ ] 1.4 实现 `build_image(self, dockerfile_path: Path, context_path: Path, image_name: str, tag: str = \"latest\", build_args: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Dict[str, str]`：\n  - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n  - 记录 `start_time = time.time()`\n  - 调用 `client.images.build(path=str(context_path), dockerfile=str(dockerfile_path), tag=f\"{image_name}:{tag}\", buildargs=build_args)`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-021/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775854346965,"end":1775854346970}}}}
