{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775854530541,"sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","part":{"id":"prt_d792b70f6001gyXLlmlPdg2apm","messageID":"msg_d792b27dc001Atj9sKx4vmH4wT","sessionID":"ses_286d7bf5effezn8f6G9VP0lIdu","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_05061aa9a0244fb081d7a10b","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-022 — CLI publish 命令 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** cmd/cli\n> **Language:** Python\n> **Size:** L\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-022/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-022/design.md`, `changes/AR-022/delta-spec.md`, `cli-toolkit/design.md`, `cli-toolkit/spec.md`\n\n## T1. 扩展 DockerService — 镜像推送支持\n\n- [ ] 1.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py` 中实现 `push_image(self, image_tag: str, registry_url: str, username: Optional[str] = None, password: Optional[str] = None) -> Dict[str, str]`：\n  - 使用 `docker.from_env()` 创建客户端\n  - 调用 `client.images.push(repository, tag, auth_config)` 推送镜像\n  - 返回 `{\"pushed_image\": image_tag, \"status\": \"success\"}`\n- [ ] 1.2 实现 `_docker_login_sdk(self, registry_url: str, username: str, password: str) -> bool`：\n  - 调用 `client.login(username, password, registry_url)`\n  - 成功返回 `True`，失败抛出异常\n- [ ] 1.3 实现 `_tag_image_sdk(self, source_image: str, target_image: str) -> bool`：\n  - 调用 `client.images.get(source_image).tag(target_image)`\n  - 成功返回 `True`\n- [ ] 1.4 在 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py` 中添加测试：\n  - `TestDockerService_PushImage_Success`：成功推送 → 返回正确结果\n  - `TestDockerService_PushImage_WithCredentials`：带 credentials 推送 → `auth_config` 正确传递\n  - `TestDockerService_PushImage_Failure`：推送失败 → 抛出 `docker.errors.APIError`\n  - `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Success`：登录成功 → 返回 `True`\n  - `TestDockerService_DockerLoginSdk_Failure`：登录失败 → 抛出异常\n  - `TestDockerService_TagImageSdk_Success`：tag 成功 → 返回 `True`\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_docker_service.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T2. 实现 AgentCubeProvider — AgentRuntime CR 部署\n\n- [ ] 2.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`\n- [ ] 2.2 定义 `AgentCubeProvider` 类：`__init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False)`\n- [ ] 2.3 实现 `deploy_agent_runtime(self, agent_name: str, image_url: str, port: int, entrypoint: str, env_vars: Dict[str, str], workload_manager_url: str, router_url: str, readiness_probe_path: str, readiness_probe_port: int) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n  - 初始化 K8s client（`kubernetes.client.CustomObjectsApi`）\n  - 构造 AgentRuntime CR spec（`runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）\n  - CR 包含：image、port、entrypoint、env、workload_manager_url、router_url、readinessProbe\n  - sessionTimeout=15m、maxSessionDuration=8h\n  - imagePullSecrets=[{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}]\n  - 调用 `create_namespaced_custom_object` 创建 CR\n  - 返回 `{\"name\": sanitized_name, \"endpoint\": router_url + \"/v1/...\"}`\n- [ ] 2.4 实现 `_sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str`：\n  - 将无效字符替换为 `-`\n  - 截断至 63 字符（K8s 名称限制）\n- [ ] 2.5 实现 `get_agent_runtime(self, name: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]`：\n  - 调用 `get_namespaced_custom_object` 获取现有 CR\n  - 不存在时返回 `None`\n- [ ] 2.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py`\n- [ ] 2.7 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_DeployCR`：创建 AgentRuntime CR，spec 正确\n- [ ] 2.8 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_EnvVarFallback`：缺失 env vars 时 fallback 到 `os.environ`\n- [ ] 2.9 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_SessionConfig`：CR 包含 sessionTimeout=15m, maxSessionDuration=8h\n- [ ] 2.10 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_ImagePullSecrets`：CR 包含 imagePullSecrets\n- [ ] 2.11 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_SanitizeName`：无效字符替换，截断至 63 字符\n- [ ] 2.12 测试 `TestAgentCubeProvider_GetAgentRuntime`：获取现有 CR\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T3. 实现 KubernetesProvider — Deployment + NodePort Service 部署\n\n- [ ] 3.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`\n- [ ] 3.2 定义 `KubernetesProvider` 类：`__init__(self, namespace: str = \"default\", verbose: bool = False)`\n- [ ] 3.3 实现 `deploy_agent(self, agent_name: str, image_url: str, port: int, entrypoint: str, replicas: int = 1, node_port: Optional[int] = None, env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n  - 初始化 K8s client（`kubernetes.client.AppsV1Api`, `CoreV1Api`）\n  - 创建 Deployment（container: image, port, entrypoint, env, replicas）\n  - 创建 NodePort Service（port 映射，node_port 指定或自动分配）\n  - 返回 `{\"deployment_name\": name, \"service_name\": name, \"service_url\": f\"http://localhost:{actual_node_port}\", \"node_port\": actual_node_port}`\n- [ ] 3.4 实现 `wait_for_deployment_ready(self, deployment_name: str, timeout: int = 120) -> None`：\n  - 轮询 Deployment status（`read_namespaced_deployment_status`）\n  - 检查 `ready_replicas == replicas`\n  - 超时则抛出 `TimeoutError`\n- [ ] 3.5 实现 `delete_agent(self, agent_name: str) -> None`：\n  - 删除 Deployment + Service\n  - 404 时忽略（`client.rest.ApiException` status=404）\n- [ ] 3.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py`\n- [ ] 3.7 测试 `TestK8sProvider_DeployAgent`：创建 Deployment + NodePort Service\n- [ ] 3.8 测试 `TestK8sProvider_WaitForReady`：等待至 ready 后返回\n- [ ] 3.9 测试 `TestK8sProvider_WaitTimeout`：超时 → `TimeoutError`\n- [ ] 3.10 测试 `TestK8sProvider_NodePortRange`：NodePort 在 30000-32767 范围\n- [ ] 3.11 测试 `TestK8sProvider_ServiceUrl`：URL 格式 `http://localhost:{node_port}`\n- [ ] 3.12 测试 `TestK8sProvider_DeleteAgent`：删除 Deployment + Service，忽略 404\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T4. 实现 PublishRuntime 类骨架与 publish() 主编排方法\n\n- [ ] 4.1 创建 `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`\n- [ ] 4.2 定义 `PublishRuntime` 类：`__init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\")`，存储 `self.verbose` 和 `self.provider`\n- [ ] 4.3 实现 `publish(self, workspace_path: Path, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]` 主编排方法：\n  - 1. 校验 workspace 路径存在且为目录 → 否则 `ValueError`\n  - 2. 加载元数据：`metadata = MetadataService(verbose=self.verbose).load_metadata(workspace_path)`，如为 None 则 `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged. Run 'pack' first.\")`\n  - 3. 应用 CLI 选项覆盖：遍历 `[\"version\", \"description\", \"region\"]`，非 None 则 `setattr(metadata, key, value)`\n  - 4. 校验 node_port 范围（如提供）：不在 30000-32767 → `ValueError(\"NodePort must be between 30000 and 32767\")`\n  - 5. 准备镜像：`image_url = self._prepare_image_for_publishing(workspace_path, metadata, options)`\n  - 6. 路由到 provider：`agentcube` → `_publish_cr_to_k8s()`，`k8s` → `_publish_k8s()`，其他 → `ValueError`\n  - 7. 更新元数据：`self._update_publish_metadata(workspace_path, result)`\n  - 8. 返回 result\n- [ ] 4.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py`\n- [ ] 4.5 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_MissingWorkspace`：路径不存在 → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 4.6 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_UnpackagedWorkspace`：无 `agent_metadata.yaml` → `ValueError(\"Workspace has not been packaged...\")`\n- [ ] 4.7 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_UnsupportedProvider`：provider=\"unknown\" → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 4.8 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_UnsupportedBuildMode`：build_mode=\"unknown\" → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 4.9 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_InvalidNodePort_Below`：node_port=29999 → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 4.10 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_InvalidNodePort_Above`：node_port=32768 → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 4.11 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_VersionOverride`：`--version v2.0.0` → metadata.version 更新\n- [ ] 4.12 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_DescriptionOverride`：`--description` → metadata.description 更新\n- [ ] 4.13 测试 `TestPublishRuntime_RegionOverride`：`--region cn-north-4` → metadata.region 更新\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"MissingWorkspace or UnpackagedWorkspace or UnsupportedProvider or UnsupportedBuildMode or InvalidNodePort or Override\"` 全部通过（T5-T7 方法可用 mock 替代）\n\n---\n\n## T5. 实现镜像准备流程 — PublishRuntime._prepare_image_for_publishing 及子方法\n\n- [ ] 5.1 实现 `_prepare_image_for_publishing(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str`：\n  - `metadata.build_mode == \"local\"` → 调用 `_prepare_local_image`\n  - `metadata.build_mode == \"cloud\"` → 调用 `_prepare_cloud_image`\n  - 其他 → `ValueError(f\"Unsupported build mode: {metadata.build_mode}\")`\n- [ ] 5.2 实现 `_prepare_local_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str`：\n  - 创建 `DockerService` 实例\n  - 检查 Docker 可用性 → 不可用则 `RuntimeError(\"Docker is not available or not running\")`\n  - 检查 `image_url`（CLI 选项）→ 无则检查 metadata.image → 仍无则 `ValueError(\"Image URL is required for local build mode\")`\n  - 构建 image_tag：`f\"{image_url}:{metadata.version or 'latest'}\"`\n  - 如提供 credentials（CLI 或 metadata）→ 调用 `docker_service._docker_login_sdk`\n  - 调用 `docker_service.push_image` 推送\n  - 返回推送后的 image reference\n- [ ] 5.3 实现 `_prepare_cloud_image(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, options: Dict[str, Any]) -> str`：\n  - 优先使用 `options.get(\"image_url\")`\n  - 其次使用 `metadata.image.get(\"url\")`\n  - 均无则 `ValueError(\"Image URL is required for cloud build mode\")`\n  - 返回 image reference（不执行 Docker 操作）\n- [ ] 5.4 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_image.py`\n- [ ] 5.5 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_Success`：local 模式，Docker 可用，image_url 提供 → 推送成功\n- [ ] 5.6 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_NoImageUrl`：local 模式，无 image_url → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 5.7 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_DockerUnavailable`：local 模式，Docker 不可用 → `RuntimeError`\n- [ ] 5.8 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_WithCredentials`：提供 credentials → `_docker_login_sdk` 被调用\n- [ ] 5.9 测试 `TestPrepareImage_LocalMode_MetadataCredentials`：CLI 无 credentials，metadata 有 → 使用 metadata credentials\n- [ ] 5.10 测试 `TestPrepareImage_CloudMode_Success`：cloud 模式，image_url 提供 → 直接返回\n- [ ] 5.11 测试 `TestPrepareImage_CloudMode_FromMetadata`：cloud 模式，image URL 从 metadata.image[\"url\"] 解析\n- [ ] 5.12 测试 `TestPrepareImage_CloudMode_NoUrl`：cloud 模式，无 image URL → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 5.13 测试 `TestPrepareImage_UnknownBuildMode`：build_mode=\"unknown\" → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 5.14 测试 `TestPrepareImage_Dispatch_Local`：build_mode=\"local\" → 调用 `_prepare_local_image`\n- [ ] 5.15 测试 `TestPrepareImage_Dispatch_Cloud`：build_mode=\"cloud\" → 调用 `_prepare_cloud_image`\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_image.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §Image preparation 全部场景\n\n---\n\n## T6. 实现 AgentCube provider 发布流程 — PublishRuntime._publish_cr_to_k8s\n\n- [ ] 6.1 实现 `_publish_cr_to_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n  - 校验 prerequisites：`metadata.router_url` 和 `metadata.workload_manager_url` 均存在 → 否则 `ValueError(\"router_url and workload_manager_url are required...\")`\n  - 校验 readiness probe：`metadata.readiness_probe_path` 和 `metadata.readiness_probe_port` 均存在 → 否则 `ValueError`\n  - 初始化 `AgentCubeProvider(namespace=options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\", verbose=self.verbose)`\n  - 调用 `provider.deploy_agent_runtime(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, env_vars, workload_manager_url, router_url, readiness_probe_path, readiness_probe_port)`\n  - 返回 `{\"agent_id\": result[\"name\"], \"agent_endpoint\": result[\"endpoint\"], \"namespace\": namespace, \"k8s_deployment\": {\"type\": \"AgentRuntime\", \"namespace\": namespace, \"cr_name\": result[\"name\"]}}`\n- [ ] 6.2 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` 中添加测试：\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_ValidAgentCubePublish`：有效 workspace，agentcube provider → 成功发布 CR\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingRouterUrl`：agentcube provider，无 router_url → `ValueError`\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingWorkloadManagerUrl`：agentcube provider，无 workload_manager_url → `ValueError`\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingReadinessProbePath`：agentcube provider，无 readiness_probe_path → `ValueError`\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_MissingReadinessProbePort`：agentcube provider，无 readiness_probe_port → `ValueError`\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_AgentCubeWithNamespace`：`--namespace production` → 使用指定 namespace\n- [ ] 6.3 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py` 中添加测试：\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_AgentCubeMetadataUpdate`：发布成功后 metadata 包含 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment（type=\"AgentRuntime\"）\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"AgentCube\"` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T7. 实现 K8s provider 发布流程 — PublishRuntime._publish_k8s\n\n- [ ] 7.1 实现 `_publish_k8s(self, workspace_path: Path, metadata, **options: Any) -> Dict[str, Any]`：\n  - 解析 `namespace = options.get(\"namespace\") or \"default\"`\n  - 解析 `replicas = options.get(\"replicas\") or 1`\n  - 解析 `node_port = options.get(\"node_port\")`\n  - 初始化 `KubernetesProvider(namespace=namespace, verbose=self.verbose)`\n  - 调用 `provider.deploy_agent(agent_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, replicas, node_port, env_vars)`\n  - 调用 `provider.wait_for_deployment_ready(deployment_name, timeout=120)`\n  - 超时则 `RuntimeError(f\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within 120s\")`\n  - 返回 `{\"deployment_name\": result[\"deployment_name\"], \"service_name\": result[\"service_name\"], \"service_url\": result[\"service_url\"], \"namespace\": namespace, \"replicas\": replicas, \"node_port\": result[\"node_port\"], \"k8s_deployment\": {\"type\": \"Deployment\", \"namespace\": namespace, \"deployment_name\": result[\"deployment_name\"], \"service_url\": result[\"service_url\"]}}`\n- [ ] 7.2 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` 中添加测试：\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_ValidK8sPublish`：有效 workspace，k8s provider → 成功发布 Deployment + Service\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_DeploymentTimeout`：K8s 部署未 ready → `RuntimeError`\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sWithReplicas`：`--replicas 3` → 传递 replicas=3\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sWithNodePort`：`--node-port 30080` → service_url 为 `http://localhost:30080`\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sWithNamespace`：`--namespace staging` → 使用指定 namespace\n- [ ] 7.3 在 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py` 中添加测试：\n  - `TestPublishRuntime_K8sMetadataUpdate`：发布成功后 metadata 包含 k8s_deployment（type=\"Deployment\", deployment_name, service_url）\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py -v -k \"K8s\"` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T8. 实现发布元数据更新 — PublishRuntime._update_publish_metadata\n\n- [ ] 8.1 实现 `_update_publish_metadata(self, workspace_path: Path, agent_info: Dict[str, Any]) -> None`：\n  - 创建 `MetadataService(verbose=self.verbose)` 实例\n  - 构造 updates dict：\n    ```python\n    updates = {\n        \"agent_id\": agent_info.get(\"agent_id\"),\n        \"agent_endpoint\": agent_info.get(\"agent_endpoint\") or agent_info.get(\"service_url\"),\n        \"k8s_deployment\": agent_info.get(\"k8s_deployment\"),\n    }\n    ```\n  - 调用 `service.update_metadata(workspace_path, updates)`\n- [ ] 8.2 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py`\n- [ ] 8.3 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_AgentCube`：agentcube 发布 → metadata.agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment.type=\"AgentRuntime\"\n- [ ] 8.4 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_K8s`：k8s 发布 → metadata.agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment.type=\"Deployment\"\n- [ ] 8.5 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_Persisted`：更新后重新加载 → 数据一致\n- [ ] 8.6 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_ServiceUrlFallback`：无 agent_endpoint 时使用 service_url\n- [ ] 8.7 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_K8sDeploymentStructure`：k8s_deployment 包含 type, deployment_name, namespace, service_url\n- [ ] 8.8 测试 `TestUpdatePublishMetadata_AgentCubeDeploymentStructure`：k8s_deployment 包含 type, agent_name, namespace, agent_id\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime_metadata.py -v` 全部通过\n\n---\n\n## T9. 实现 CLI publish 命令入口 — agentcube/cli/main.py\n\n- [ ] 9.1 在 `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` 中添加导入：\n  - `from agentcube.runtime.publish_runtime import PublishRuntime`\n- [ ] 9.2 实现 `@app.command()` publish 命令，选项：\n  - `workspace: str = typer.Option(\".\", \"-f\", \"--workspace\", ...)`\n  - `version: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--version\", ...)`\n  - `image_url: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-url\", ...)`\n  - `image_username: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-username\", ...)`\n  - `image_password: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--image-password\", ...)`\n  - `description: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--description\", ...)`\n  - `region: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--region\", ...)`\n  - `cloud_provider: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--cloud-provider\", ...)`\n  - `provider: str = typer.Option(\"agentcube\", \"--provider\", ...)`\n  - `node_port: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--node-port\", ...)`\n  - `replicas: Optional[int] = typer.Option(None, \"--replicas\", ...)`\n  - `namespace: Optional[str] = typer.Option(None, \"--namespace\", ...)`\n  - `verbose: bool = typer.Option(False, \"--verbose\", ...)`\n- [ ] 9.3 命令体：\n  - 校验 workspace 路径存在且为目录 → 否则 `ValueError`\n  - 校验 provider 值（`agentcube` 或 `k8s`）→ 否则 `ValueError`\n  - 校验 node_port 范围（如提供）→ 30000-32767，否则 `ValueError`\n  - 使用 Rich `Progress` + `SpinnerColumn` 显示 `\"Publishing agent...\"`\n  - 调用 `PublishRuntime(verbose=verbose, provider=provider).publish(workspace_path, **options)`\n  - 成功时 Rich 输出（agentcube provider）：agent name, workspace path, agent ID, endpoint URL\n  - 成功时 Rich 输出（k8s provider）：agent name, workspace path, deployment name, service name, service URL\n  - 异常时调用 `_handle_error(e, \"publishing agent\", verbose)`\n- [ ] 9.4 更新 `agentcube/__init__.py` 导出：添加 `PublishRuntime`\n- [ ] 9.5 更新 `agentcube/runtime/__init__.py` 重新导出 `PublishRuntime`\n- [ ] 9.6 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_publish_command.py`\n- [ ] 9.7 测试 `TestPublishCommand_DefaultOptions`：无选项 → workspace=\".\", provider=\"agentcube\"\n- [ ] 9.8 测试 `TestPublishCommand_CustomWorkspace`：`-f /path` → 使用指定路径\n- [ ] 9.9 测试 `TestPublishCommand_AllOptions`：传递全部选项 → 正确传递给 PublishRuntime\n- [ ] 9.10 测试 `TestPublishCommand_SuccessAgentCube`：agentcube provider → 成功输出 agent name, agent ID, endpoint\n- [ ] 9.11 测试 `TestPublishCommand_SuccessK8s`：k8s provider → 成功输出 deployment name, service name, service URL\n- [ ] 9.12 测试 `TestPublishCommand_ErrorNoVerbose`：失败无 verbose → 红色错误，无 traceback，exit 1\n- [ ] 9.13 测试 `TestPublishCommand_ErrorVerbose`：失败有 verbose → 红色错误 + traceback，exit 1\n- [ ] 9.14 测试 `TestPublishCommand_ProgressSpinner`：执行期间显示 Progress spinner\n- [ ] 9.15 测试 `TestPublishCommand_HelpOutput`：`publish --help` 显示全部 13 个选项\n- [ ] 9.16 测试 `TestPublishCommand_InvalidProvider`：`--provider invalid` → `ValueError`\n- [ ] 9.17 测试 `TestPublishCommand_InvalidNodePort`：`--node-port 9999` → `ValueError`\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_publish_command.py -v` 全部通过；覆盖 delta-spec §CLI success output、§Error handling、§Progress indication 全部场景\n\n---\n\n## T10. 端到端集成测试\n\n- [ ] 10.1 创建 `cmd/cli/tests/integration/test_publish_e2e.py`\n- [ ] 10.2 测试 `TestPublishE2E_AgentCube_FullFlow`：对已 pack+build 的 hello-agent 运行 publish（agentcube provider，mock K8s）→ 成功\n- [ ] 10.3 测试 `TestPublishE2E_K8s_FullFlow`：对已 pack+build 的工作区运行 publish（k8s provider，mock K8s）→ 成功\n- [ ] 10.4 测试 `TestPublishE2E_UnpackagedWorkspace`：对未 pack 的工作区运行 publish → 错误退出\n- [ ] 10.5 测试 `TestPublishE2E_CliOverrides`：使用 `--version`, `--namespace`, `--replicas` 覆盖 → 正确传递\n- [ ] 10.6 测试 `TestPublishE2E_InvalidWorkspace`：对非目录路径运行 publish → 错误退出\n- [ ] 10.7 测试 `TestPublishE2E_MetadataUpdated`：publish 成功后 → `agent_metadata.yaml` 包含 agent_id, agent_endpoint, k8s_deployment\n- [ ] 10.8 测试 `TestPublishE2E_LocalModeImagePush`：local build mode + `--image-url` → 镜像推送流程触发（mock Docker）\n\n**Verification:** `pytest cmd/cli/tests/integration/test_publish_e2e.py -v` 全部通过（K8s/Docker 依赖的测试可标记 skip）\n\n---\n\n## T11. 代码质量门禁与最终验证\n\n- [ ] 11.1 运行 `ruff check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无 lint 错误\n- [ ] 11.2 运行 `ruff format --check cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认格式合规\n- [ ] 11.3 运行 `mypy cmd/cli/agentcube/` 确认无类型错误\n- [ ] 11.4 运行 `pytest cmd/cli/tests/ -v --cov=agentcube --cov-report=term-missing` 确认覆盖率 ≥ 80%\n- [ ] 11.5 确认 T/C 比率 > 0.4（测试代码行数 / 源代码行数）\n- [ ] 11.6 运行 `pip install -e cmd/cli[dev]` 确认安装成功\n- [ ] 11.7 运行 `kubectl-agentcube --help` 确认帮助输出包含 publish 命令\n- [ ] 11.8 运行 `kubectl-agentcube publish --help` 确认 publish 选项完整（workspace, version, image-url, image-username, im